<noinclude>
This is the "Binding" template.
It should be called in the following format:
<pre>
{{Binding
|Binding.Local role=
|Binding.Bound role=
}}
</pre>
Note that the role names should be in the Frame.Role format so as to be able to resolve the
role's location.
Edit the page to see the template text.
</noinclude>
<includeonly>{| class="wikitable" style="margin: 0px 2em 2px;"
| scope="col" width="300"| {{{Binding.Local role|}}}={{{Binding.Bound role|}}} {{#set:Binding={{{Binding.Local role|}}};{{{Binding.Bound role|}}}}}
|}</includeonly>
